---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Why Blue Logic - The Value Difference"
  description="$15,000 vs $30,000. Same professional quality, half the price. See how we deliver premium RO systems without the premium markup."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The $15k Value Proposition</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Professional quality without the inflated price tag
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="comparison">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Blue Logic vs. The Competition</h2>
      <p class="intro">
        We deliver the same professional-grade components and installation
        quality as competitors charging $30,000+. Here's how we do it—and why
        you shouldn't pay more.
      </p>

      <div class="comparison-table">
        <div class="comparison-row header">
          <div class="feature">Feature</div>
          <div class="blue-logic">Blue Logic</div>
          <div class="competitors">Competitors</div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-row">
          <div class="feature">Price</div>
          <div class="blue-logic highlight">$15,000</div>
          <div class="competitors">$30,000+</div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-row">
          <div class="feature">Professional Installation</div>
          <div class="blue-logic">✓ Included</div>
          <div class="competitors">✓ Included</div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-row">
          <div class="feature">Commercial-Grade Components</div>
          <div class="blue-logic">✓ Yes</div>
          <div class="competitors">✓ Yes</div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-row">
          <div class="feature">Compact Footprint</div>
          <div class="blue-logic highlight">50% smaller</div>
          <div class="competitors">Standard bulk</div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-row">
          <div class="feature">Noise Level</div>
          <div class="blue-logic highlight">10x quieter</div>
          <div class="competitors">Standard</div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-row">
          <div class="feature">Marketing & Overhead</div>
          <div class="blue-logic highlight">Minimal</div>
          <div class="competitors">Heavy markup</div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-row">
          <div class="feature">Local Service</div>
          <div class="blue-logic">✓ Wasatch Front</div>
          <div class="competitors">✓ Various</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="value-breakdown">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why We Can Charge Half</h2>

      <div class="value-cards">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Direct Business Model</h3>
          <p>
            We cut out the middlemen and excessive marketing spend. No celebrity
            endorsements, no massive ad campaigns—just word of mouth and
            exceptional service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Efficient Engineering</h3>
          <p>
            Our compact design uses advanced engineering to reduce material
            costs and installation time without sacrificing quality or
            performance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Local Focus</h3>
          <p>
            By serving only the Wasatch Front, we optimize logistics, reduce
            overhead, and build deep relationships with suppliers and customers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Fair Pricing Philosophy</h3>
          <p>
            We believe premium water shouldn't require premium income. Our
            pricing reflects our actual costs plus a fair margin—nothing more.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="protection">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What You're Protecting Against</h2>
      <p class="intro">
        Clean water isn't just about taste. It's about removing invisible
        threats that affect your family's health, your home's longevity, and
        your peace of mind.
      </p>

      <div class="threat-cards">
        <div class="threat-card">
          <div class="threat-icon">⚗️</div>
          <h3>PFAS & Forever Chemicals</h3>
          <p>
            Industrial chemicals that persist in the environment and accumulate
            in your body. Linked to cancer, hormone disruption, and immune
            system damage—found in water supplies across Utah.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="threat-card">
          <div class="threat-icon">🧬</div>
          <h3>Microplastics</h3>
          <p>
            Microscopic plastic fragments detected in tap water, bottled water,
            and even human blood. These particles carry toxins and accumulate
            over time with unknown long-term effects.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="threat-card">
          <div class="threat-icon">🚿</div>
          <h3>Transdermal Absorption</h3>
          <p>
            Toxins don't just enter through drinking. During showers and baths,
            your skin absorbs chemicals, and your lungs inhale vaporized
            contaminants—whole-home filtration stops them at every tap.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="threat-card">
          <div class="threat-icon">🔧</div>
          <h3>Hard Water & Scale Damage</h3>
          <p>
            Calcium and magnesium minerals create scale buildup that reduces
            appliance lifespan, clogs pipes, and wastes money on soap and
            repairs. Utah's hard water is among the hardest in the nation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="threat-card">
          <div class="threat-icon">☣️</div>
          <h3>Chlorine & Byproducts</h3>
          <p>
            Municipal water treatment chemicals and their disinfection
            byproducts can irritate skin, exacerbate respiratory conditions, and
            have been associated with increased cancer risk.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="protection-summary">
        Our whole-home RO system addresses all five of these threats—not just at
        your kitchen sink, but at every faucet, shower, and appliance in your
        home.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="guarantee">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Blue Logic Guarantee</h2>
      <p class="guarantee-text">
        We use the exact same commercial-grade components as competitors. We
        provide the same professional installation. We offer the same
        comprehensive warranties. The only difference? We don't believe in
        charging twice what's fair.
      </p>
      <div class="guarantee-badges">
        <div class="badge">
          <strong>Professional Installation</strong>
          <p>Licensed & certified technicians</p>
        </div>
        <div class="badge">
          <strong>Grade-A Components</strong>
          <p>Commercial-quality materials</p>
        </div>
        <div class="badge">
          <strong>Full Warranty</strong>
          <p>Comprehensive coverage included</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container center">
      <h2>Ready to Save $15,000?</h2>
      <p>Get a free consultation and water quality assessment</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button">Schedule Your Audit</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      oklch(0.95 0.01 90) 0%,
      oklch(0.85 0.05 220) 100%
    );
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .container.center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  .comparison {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .comparison-table {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .comparison-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .comparison-row:not(:last-child) {
    border-bottom: 1px solid oklch(0.9 0.01 90);
  }

  .comparison-row.header {
    background-color: oklch(0.2 0.02 270);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .feature {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .blue-logic,
  .competitors {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .value-breakdown {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
  }

  .value-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
  }

  .value-card p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  .protection {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .threat-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .threat-card {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
  }

  .threat-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .threat-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: oklch(0.2 0.02 270);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .threat-card p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .protection-summary {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    color: oklch(0.3 0.02 270);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: oklch(0.95 0.05 220);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .guarantee {
    background-color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .guarantee-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
  }

  .guarantee-badges {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .badge {
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .badge strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: oklch(0.2 0.02 270);
  }

  .badge p {
    color: oklch(0.5 0.02 270);
  }

  .cta-section {
    background-color: oklch(0.98 0.01 90);
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: oklch(0.4 0.02 270);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: oklch(0.7 0.1 220);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .comparison-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .comparison-row.header {
      display: none;
    }

    .feature::before {
      content: attr(data-label);
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
  }
</style>
